Package: RentCalculatoR
Type: Package
Title: CHANGES IN RENTS CALCULATOR (FOR SWITZERLAND)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ruth Peterhans ruth.maria.peterhans@usi.ch, Giuliano Giovanardi, giuliano.giovanardi@usi.ch
Maintainer: The package maintainer <ruthmp@usi.ch>
Description: With the package RentCalculatoR you can calculate the change in rent of residential real estate according to Swiss law. Changes in value-adding investments, depreciation, interests and reference interest rates can be taken into account. As well as changings due to changes in the market such as inflation, mortgage and cost increments.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: xml2, rvest, readr, readxl, tidyr, zoo, magrittr

Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder:knitr

LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
